Hospitals Arrears

This work was developed to explore the arrears of Portuguese Public Hospitals between 2014-2019, all the data in publicly available at “Portal da Transparencia”

Set the configurations

Load the dataset

We loaded the databases from the API of the transparency Portal of the Ministry of Health, each time we run the code routine the latest data is loaded.
